Global Antimicrobial Coated Duct Market Insights
Antimicrobial Coated Duct Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Antimicrobial Coated Duct Market Overview
The antimicrobial coated duct market is experiencing significant growth, with a market value expected to reach USD 1.5 billion by 2026, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2021. These ducts are used primarily in HVAC systems and are designed to reduce microbial growth, thereby enhancing air quality in residential, commercial, and industrial settings. The increasing demand for clean air solutions, coupled with stringent regulations for air hygiene, is propelling market growth. The rising awareness of health and safety issues, especially in healthcare and hospitality sectors, further fuels this market expansion.

